snippet: The Aquabats, an indescribably odd group of musicians who first got together in the 1990s, have their work cut out for them in their newest venture, “The Aquabats! Super Show!”
abstract: Neil Genzlinger reviews Hub channel comedy series The Aquabats! Super Show!, featuring rock band The Aquabats.
